## peek() function

Transducer version of , i.e. extracts the last item of an array.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare function peek<T>(): Transducer<T[], T>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`Transducer<T[], T>`

## Example


```ts
[...peek([ [1, 2, 3], [4, 5] ])]
// [ 3, 5 ]

```
